      "prompt_template": {
        "description": "LLM提示词模板，用于帮助模型理解此配方类型 / LLM prompt template to help the model understand this recipe type",
        "template": "这是 Minecraft 原版的有序合成配方类型。需要在工作台上按照特定的模式摆放材料。\n\n关键特征：\n- 需要使用pattern（模式）和key（键值对）定义摆放方式\n- pattern是1-3行的字符串数组，每个字符代表一个位置\n- key定义每个字符对应的物品或标签\n- 适合需要特定形状或位置的合成（如工具、装备、方块）\n\n判断标准：\n1. 如果配方有明确的形状或图案，必须使用此类型\n2. 如果是工具、武器、装备的制作，通常使用此类型\n3. 如果原配方已经是有序合成，保持使用此类型\n\n典型应用场景：\n- 木棍：2个木板竖直摆放\n- 箱子：8个木板围成空心方块\n- 剑：2个材料+1个木棍，竖直排列\n- 镐：3个材料横排+2个木棍竖直\n\npattern格式说明：\n- 每行最多3个字符，最多3行\n- 空格表示空位置\n- 相同字符表示相同物品\n- 示例：[\"##\", \"##\"] 表示2x2的方块\n\n注意事项：\n- 如果配方不需要特定位置，应该使用shapeless（无序合成）\n- pattern应该尽可能简洁（移除不必要的空行和空列）\n- key中的物品可以使用tag（标签）来支持多种相似物品\n\nThis is Minecraft vanilla shaped crafting recipe type. Requires materials to be placed in a specific pattern on the crafting table.\n\nKey characteristics:\n- Uses pattern and key to define placement\n- pattern is 1-3 rows of strings, each character represents a position\n- key defines what item or tag each character represents\n- Suitable for crafting requiring specific shape or position (tools, equipment, blocks)\n\nJudgment criteria:\n1. If recipe has clear shape or pattern, must use this type\n2. If crafting tools, weapons, equipment, usually use this type\n3. If original recipe is already shaped crafting, keep using this type\n\nTypical use cases:\n- Stick: 2 planks placed vertically\n- Chest: 8 planks forming hollow square\n- Sword: 2 materials + 1 stick, vertical arrangement\n- Pickaxe: 3 materials horizontal + 2 sticks vertical\n\nPattern format:\n- Max 3 characters per row, max 3 rows\n- Space represents empty position\n- Same character represents same item\n- Example: [\"##\", \"##\"] represents 2x2 square\n\nNotes:\n- If recipe doesn't require specific position, should use shapeless\n- Pattern should be as concise as possible (remove unnecessary empty rows/columns)\n- Items in key can use tags to support multiple similar items"
      },
      "examples": [
        {
          "name": "木棍 / Stick",
          "recipe": {
            "type": "minecraft:crafting_shaped",
            "pattern": [
              "#",
              "#"
            ],
            "key": {
              "#": {
                "tag": "minecraft:planks"
              }
            },
            "result": {
              "item": "minecraft:stick",
              "count": 4
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "箱子 / Chest",
          "recipe": {
            "type": "minecraft:crafting_shaped",
            "pattern": [
              "###",
              "# #",
              "###"
            ],
            "key": {
              "#": {
                "tag": "minecraft:planks"
              }
            },
            "result": {
              "item": "minecraft:chest"
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
