      "prompt_template": {
        "description": "LLM提示词模板，用于帮助模型理解此配方类型 / LLM prompt template to help the model understand this recipe type",
        "template": "这是 Minecraft 原版的无序合成配方类型。材料可以在工作台上任意摆放，不需要特定位置。\n\n关键特征：\n- 使用ingredients数组列出所有材料\n- 材料摆放顺序和位置无关紧要\n- 适合简单的组合、混合类配方\n- 最多支持9种材料（3x3工作台）\n\n判断标准：\n1. 如果配方只是简单地把材料组合在一起，使用此类型\n2. 如果材料的摆放位置不影响结果，必须使用此类型\n3. 如果是染料、简单食物、材料转换，通常使用此类型\n\n典型应用场景：\n- 面包：3个小麦（位置任意）\n- 染料混合：2种染料组合（位置任意）\n- 糖：1个甘蔗（简单转换）\n- 火药：硝石+煤炭+沙子（位置任意）\n\ningredients格式说明：\n- 是一个数组，每个元素代表一种材料\n- 可以使用item指定具体物品\n- 可以使用tag指定标签（支持多种相似物品）\n- 数量通过重复元素来表示（如3个小麦就写3次）\n\n与shaped（有序合成）的区别：\n- shapeless: 材料位置无关，适合简单组合\n- shaped: 材料必须按特定模式摆放，适合有形状的物品\n\n注意事项：\n- 不要对需要特定形状的配方（如工具、装备）使用无序合成\n- 对于复杂食物的制作，考虑使用farmersdelight:cooking而非shapeless\n- 对于合金制作，考虑使用create:mixing而非shapeless\n\nThis is Minecraft vanilla shapeless crafting recipe type. Materials can be placed anywhere on the crafting table, no specific position required.\n\nKey characteristics:\n- Uses ingredients array to list all materials\n- Material placement order and position don't matter\n- Suitable for simple combination/mixing recipes\n- Supports up to 9 materials (3x3 crafting table)\n\nJudgment criteria:\n1. If recipe simply combines materials together, use this type\n2. If material placement position doesn't affect result, must use this type\n3. If for dyes, simple food, material conversion, usually use this type\n\nTypical use cases:\n- Bread: 3 wheat (any position)\n- Dye mixing: 2 dyes combined (any position)\n- Sugar: 1 sugar cane (simple conversion)\n- Gunpowder: saltpeter + coal + sand (any position)\n\ningredients format:\n- Is an array, each element represents one material\n- Can use item to specify specific item\n- Can use tag to specify tag (support multiple similar items)\n- Quantity represented by repeating elements (e.g., 3 wheat = write 3 times)\n\nDifference from shaped:\n- shapeless: material position irrelevant, for simple combinations\n- shaped: materials must follow specific pattern, for shaped items\n\nNotes:\n- Don't use shapeless for recipes requiring specific shape (tools, equipment)\n- For complex food making, consider farmersdelight:cooking instead of shapeless\n- For alloy making, consider create:mixing instead of shapeless"
      },
      "examples": [
        {
          "name": "面包 / Bread",
          "recipe": {
            "type": "minecraft:crafting_shapeless",
            "ingredients": [
              {
                "item": "minecraft:wheat"
              },
